    <ui:MultipleAssign sap2010:Annotation.AnnotationText="Find which quadrant the astroid is in, using Right or Left of the chosen astroid. Then calculate the slope. All astroids with the same slope are in a straight line from the starting astroid. So by removing duplicates based on slope, we are able to get the count of &quot;visible&quot; astroid for a starting astroid." DisplayName="Find best location" sap:VirtualizedContainerService.HintSize="338,231" sap2010:WorkflowViewState.IdRef="MultipleAssign_1">
